about.summary: Ceph RADOS Gateway (rgw) admin operations REST API

name: radosgw-admin
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "radosgw-admin" %}
{% set version = "1.7.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: ae91bc8462477da38ab1d07a9d40e3827a461dcb4a5bf5b1c8ed343ebdc21d2d 

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - boto
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - radosgw

about:
  home: "https://github.com/valerytschopp/python-radosgw-admin"
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Ceph RADOS Gateway (rgw) admin operations REST API"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
